text:
[Verse]
Flying high like paper planes
Dreaming big with open lanes
Crash and burn
We rise again
Catch the wind and feel the strain

[Verse 2]
Sky’s the limit
Don’t look back
Heart beats fast upon the track
Fold the edges
Take a flight
Stars are shining in the night

[Chorus]
Paper planes
We’re soaring free
In the sky
It’s you and me
Chasing dreams
We never land
Hand in hand
We take our stand

[Verse 3]
Colors splash against the sky
Close your eyes and let’s get by
Whispers in the wind so sweet
Feel the rhythm
Hear the beat

[Bridge]
Through the clouds
We navigate
Every fear
We’ll dissipate
Climbing higher
Never fall
Shout out loud
We’ve got it all

[Chorus]
Paper planes
We’re soaring free
In the sky
It’s you and me
Chasing dreams
We never land
Hand in hand
We take our stand
title: Paper Planes
